\li{\strong{\code{\startverb test-agent-trigger.sh\stopverb}} - Test if agent triggers correctly}
}
}
}

\subtree{
\title{Implementation Workflow}
\p{To create an agent for a plugin:}

\ol{
\li{Define agent purpose and triggering conditions}
\li{Choose creation method (AI-assisted or manual)}
\li{Create \code{\startverb agents/agent-name.md\stopverb} file}
\li{Write frontmatter with all required fields}
\li{Write system prompt following best practices}
\li{Include 2-4 triggering examples in description}
\li{Validate with \code{\startverb scripts/validate-agent.sh\stopverb}}
\li{Test triggering with real scenarios}
\li{Document agent in plugin README}
}

\p{Focus on clear triggering conditions and comprehensive system prompts for autonomous operation.}
}
}